WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
Tim carefully selects a piece of sustainable oak wood.

00:03.500 --> 00:06.000
He measures and marks the wood for cutting.

00:06.500 --> 00:10.000
"Traditional techniques ensure this board will last generations," Tim explains.

00:10.500 --> 00:13.000
He hand-sands the surface to bring out the natural grain.

00:13.500 --> 00:16.000
A food-safe oil finish completes the beautiful serving board.